{"title":"送别王震将军","authors":["魏巍"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"送别王震将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏巍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月廿日凌晨，思王震将军生前事，久不成寐，成诗数首，以悼念这位中国无产阶级的英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水成斗洒天山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国荒原开新天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都赞三江风光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军从未下征鞍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤军南征久闻名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万敌丛中鬼神惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千奇兵驰南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无畏将军再长征。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂顶天立地汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚信马列气凛然；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢顶逆风斗恶浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愧中华一奇男。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只信真理不信邪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然当年工人血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶杖笃笃东西走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十老翁肠内热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自君重病思绵绵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南去广州竟不还；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日举国含悲泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来送君归天山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月廿日八宝山归来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}